      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/654584989_18575150101010818_7888282561417113636_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NTQ5MDIxOTY0Njk5NzAxMw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTAwMy5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=tDhK88YGWigQ7kNvwF33NXz&amp;_nc_oc=AdrSLXWwiASBOb-7VEnlU59mBYfZsk0ey0ZkmqDaWBFA0M08maR7LZ5tYmTdl3ZnRjA&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=yeeEovoVajh2Szmqrfgxbg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afzc2N1s0UUn9mc0OLdkbOmE2SPCQwOYV9ZXk_GEg3NaSA&amp;oe=69CA257C" alt="Slide 1 fra @metropoliskbh" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/655066865_18575150110010818_8457390478344622347_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NTQ5MDIyNDUxMjM3Mzc0NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTAwMy5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=YTKURePIRuIQ7kNvwHxNRUh&amp;_nc_oc=AdpVcKcIK5F34IDpRId6of_WDFKl6I_v9TVHKE6OBMAFvb1exMmC3Bg9guzPzd6NBqY&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=yeeEovoVajh2Szmqrfgxbg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afyjo0L_4kQXrsIJMD1pNMyYKEkB_Yq2WYIwOzmj1SpAdw&amp;oe=69CA10B5" alt="Slide 2 fra @metropoliskbh" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/654008329_18575150137010818_805420527081437700_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NTQ5MDIyNjUyNTY2NDU4Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjgxNXg1Njguc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=1WwAscXyR8AQ7kNvwGJhWGF&amp;_nc_oc=AdoedU6-D5y47csTUX6sGvkzqswk7NfwKE7aK9DTO4XXMd12iAINws_Ko_s8MLz5izU&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=yeeEovoVajh2Szmqrfgxbg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afw1kXO556MnHHecV9F69qab8aMHoRvBW4nEn43ptHn6lQ&amp;oe=69CA1622" alt="Slide 3 fra @metropoliskbh" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/653722300_18575150119010818_8123511491802173276_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NTQ5MDIyNzc0MjAzODg2NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjExMzJ4Nzg5LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=K-boGXfgDHIQ7kNvwGWKnS_&amp;_nc_oc=AdqYhGAgeBOGa8ZTq0hBrLEM2tw74N2ypk2ugfvjolDQ1SHV0Ipa-QbqVBhT_wUrCVg&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=yeeEovoVajh2Szmqrfgxbg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxBFezzVstPJ-sobbEZH5OX8Fnf9P5RcBYipPukI9GAEA&amp;oe=69CA1462" alt="Slide 4 fra @metropoliskbh" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (5 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@metropoliskbh</strong></p><p>⭐ Where do we go with the pain we carry in us?<br/>
<br/>
Director Lisa Brüning creates space for what we usually do not express. In the ritual series The Circles, created for Performing Landscapes, she invites us to explore radical honesty and care.<br/>
<br/>
-”I experience that in our society there are hardly any spaces where we can express the pain that resides in us and in the state of the world.”<br/>
<br/>
She is in residency on Refshaleøen, adapting The Circles to the current situation. Because the need has not diminished.<br/>
<br/>
-”I believe we become sick and exhausted from not expressing and trying to carry alone what is not an individual matter, but a collective trauma. Trauma experts even speak of an epidemic of collective trauma.”<br/>
<br/>
💫 The Circles are not about being fixed. They are about pausing, listening, speaking. And discovering that the pain we thought we carried alone is actually shared.<br/>
<br/>
-“Perhaps change can grow when we meet the pain of a stranger and realize: Your pain is actually mine. It goes in circles - over generations.”<br/>
<br/>
📍You can practice your own radical honesty and experience others’ in May, when The Circles become part of Performing Landscapes Copenhagen — and then continues traveling across the country.<br/>
<br/>
Photos: Frej Pries Schmedes (1,2,4,5) &amp; Marine Gastineau (3)<br/>
#performinglandscapes #metropoliskbh</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DWBdC37DTxO/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
